MacOS X < 10.6:

• not supported

MacOS X Snow Leopard:

1) Install Xcode Development Tools
2) Install MacPorts from:
		http://www.macports.org/install.php
3) Open Terminal
4) Perform commands:
		sudo port install yasm
		sudo port install binutils
		sudo port install wget
		sudo port install xorg-libXaw
		sudo port install mjpegtools
5) run setup.sh

Linux:

1) check for needed packages:
		• gcc
		• yasm
		• binutils
		• wget
		• mjpegtools (png2yuv,y4mtoyuv)
2) run setup.sh
